summary: This new code file, moviepage17.html, contributes a new movie page to the system. It includes movie details, such as the movie title "Prometheus", a poster image, a summary of the movie, a video trailer embedded from YouTube, and a section for users to rate the movie. The file also introduces a menu with links to the Home, About, and Contact pages. Additionally, it includes links to CSS and JavaScript files for styling and functionality. The file enhances the system by providing a structured layout for displaying movie information and allowing user interaction through the rating feature.
